{"tid":740671,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[漫畫]五百年之箱有無人睇過?","createTime":"2018-07-13T05:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T05:16:04.000Z","uid":7877,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"304824e5e068c02b97cbdf73d10345bd4a6c4681","tid":740671,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"當你成為某個世界的神明，你會&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n有著潔癖的葉多被自己暗戀的青梅竹馬真奈拜託打掃倉庫，在收下好人卡之後卻意外在倉庫中發現了一個奇妙的箱子。箱子有一個彷彿是古代日本一樣的世界，其中也生活著很多人類。箱子中的人類看不見葉多，將干涉箱內世界的葉多奉若神明。就在這時，真奈卻從現實世界消失了.....<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.manhuagui.com/comic/23438/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.manhuagui.com%2Fcomic%2F23438%2F&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c59eb5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.manhuagui.com/comic/23438/</a><br />\n<br />\n而家更新到24話, 個題材唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abca1b0bad0bc8b959ed6b02363766bc1e6dd12d","tid":740671,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"51f15d8667fa1ecc90b126b0e40c6b4a0b421674","tid":740671,"uid":104432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"男版青梅竹馬好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然明白正常人都唔會接受到，隨隨便便就成為被捨棄既一方<br />\n但到目前既表現，某程度感覺到心理係細過個時已經好扭曲"},{"pid":"3e308a25cf2b4487c9785f1eb899d7e873460680","tid":740671,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1a97d843df56d6c31a71536c7611828abc320a77","tid":740671,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f15d8667fa1ecc90b126b0e40c6b4a0b421674","tid":740671,"uid":104432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"男版青梅竹馬好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然明白正常人都唔會接受到，隨隨便便就成為被捨棄既一方<br />\n但到目前既表現，某程度感